tentang apa-apa lagi

00:34:55.190 --> 00:34:56.520
tetapi berjauhan dengannya.

00:35:17.920 --> 00:35:18.840
Dia ada di sini.

00:35:27.970 --> 00:35:30.010
Bravo!

00:35:30.580 --> 00:35:33.580
(Wei)

00:35:39.020 --> 00:35:42.340
(Bandar Huajing)

