Jeneral Ketakutan

00:37:51.270 --> 00:37:52.520
sedang menari di atas menara pintu gerbang.

00:37:52.590 --> 00:37:54.040
Jalan ke Istana terhalang.

00:38:02.960 --> 00:38:03.800
Ambil laluan lain.

00:38:04.460 --> 00:38:09.860
(Gu Mansion)

